title: Week 12 NFL Recap: Chiefs beat Bucs, Broncos need emergency QB, playoff predictions (Football 11/30)
description:
As they do every Sunday, the Pick Six Superfriends link up late at night to recap all the action in the NFL. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech cover everything you need to know from Week 12.
Chiefs-Bucs (2:35)
Saints-Broncos (15:30)
